tables.place:
CREATE TABLE `:table_prefix_place` (
  `place_id` bigint(20) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `google_id` varchar(50) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `is_published` tinyint(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `is_active` tinyint(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `is_approved` tinyint(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `photo_file_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `poster_id` bigint(20) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `user_id` bigint(20) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `parent_id` bigint(20) NOT NULL,
  `parent_user_id` bigint(20) NOT NULL,
  `poster_type` varchar(32) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `parent_type` varchar(32) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `name` varchar(100) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `address` text,
  `profile_name` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `slug` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` datetime NOT NULL,
  `modified_at` datetime NOT NULL,
  `latitude` double DEFAULT '0',
  `longitude` double DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`place_id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `google_id` (`google_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8
